name: Death Sprinkled Donut V.8 (Pleasure)
description: Death Sprinkled Donut V.8 (Pleasure) is a text based CGI from the I AM DEATH series. It was created in 2021 and is a variation of the Death Sprinkled Donut V from 2018 by Yasmin Senkal. V.8 (pleasure) is an animation, an illustration and a reoccurring image of the series with a symbolic impact. "Nice to meet you." They said. But the pleasure is all mine.
